# Harness Eval

You are running `/harness-eval`. **minimal-interaction** pipeline: run through and output the evaluation result.

**Stop for:** ASK-class findings (Fix-First); all review subagents failed with no results.

**Do not stop for:** AUTO-FIX (fix, commit, continue); partial subagent failure (degrade); minor / INFO-only noise.

