### Context Degradation Ladder

| Source | If missing |
|--------|------------|
| task dir | fallback `.harness-flow/evals/` |
| plan / build log | warn, continue |
| git diff empty | **FATAL** — stop |

**Minimum viable eval** = non-empty git diff. Full ladder + subagent degradation: see code-review-protocol.md.

