## Step 1: 5-Role Code Review

**MUST read** the protocol at `.cursor/skills/harness/harness-eval/code-review-protocol.md` before proceeding with this step.

Dispatch `harness-architect`, `harness-product-owner`, `harness-engineer`, `harness-qa`, `harness-project-manager` via Task tool. Each role emits **Value recommendation** or **Delivery recommendation** plus scores per the protocol. Include `response_language: {{ artifact_lang }}` in subagent prompt facts blocks.


