## Step 2: Capture Learnings

After evaluation: only durable cross-session `[LEARNING]` items (confidence ≥7). **Never** log counts, PR#, hashes, scores, or task parroting.

{% if memverse_enabled == "true" %}
Parallel `manage_domain` for five `*-learning` domains (idempotent). Dedup: `search_memory` per item. `add_memories` with `[domain]` text prefix + metadata JSON (`type`, `key`, `confidence`, `source`, `role`, `task`, `files`). Prefer `upsert_memory` when exact key match needed. Parallel writes; log `LEARNING_ADD` counters. Non-blocking if MCP missing.
{% else %}
Skip — Memverse disabled.
{% endif %}

